    {"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"## Domestic CONUS UAP Cluster 2021-2026\n\nTranche 3 (PURSUE Release 03, 12 Jun 2026) shifts this collection's center of gravity from overseas CENTCOM mission reports to ==domestic NORTHCOM cases== reported by soldiers, federal agents, and civilians.\n\nNew channels: FBI field offices + AARO case memos.\nNew phenomenology: orbs launching orbs, plasma-core red spheres, shape-shifting translucent objects, kite-shaped ground objects.","x":-1320,"y":-200,"width":560,"height":420,"color":"2"},
