    {"id":"aaro-note","type":"text","text":"## AARO disposition\n\nWestern U.S. Event: signed by Director ==Jon Kosloski== (5 Jun 2026). ~60% plausibly flares; ==~40% unresolved==. A multi-hour stationary red orb is incompatible with any known flare burn-time.","x":-220,"y":1080,"width":480,"height":240,"color":"3"},
    {"id":"ica-note","type":"text","text":"## Colorado Springs disposition\n\nICA: \"possible backscattering of sunlight\" at ==low confidence==. Five trained observers vs. a diffuse cloud-illumination cause - the central tension.","x":-700,"y":880,"width":420,"height":220,"color":"3"}
